  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to develop and validate a work-model in Primary Health Care for
      identifying patients with Sleep Apnea Syndrome, based on clinical variables and an ambulatory
      monitoring study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
